Step 1 — Pehle Netflix se login karo:
bashaz login
# Browser mein: netflix@outlook.com
# Password daalo

Step 2 — Phir Mobikwik se login karo:
bashaz login
# Browser mein: mobikwik@outlook.com
# Password daalo
Dono cached ho jayenge!

Step 3 — Verify karo dono hain:
bashaz account list --output table
Output:
Name              User                    IsDefault
────────────────  ──────────────────────  ─────────
Azure Free Trial  netflix@outlook.com     True
Azure Free Trial  mobikwik@outlook.com    False

Step 4 — Switch karna:
bash# Netflix pe jaao
az account set \
  --subscription "netflix-subscription-id"

# Mobikwik pe jaao
az account set \
  --subscription "mobikwik-subscription-id"

Step 5 — Current check karo:
bashaz account show --query "user.name" --output tsv

Problem — dono ka naam same hoga:
Azure Free Trial  netflix@outlook.com
Azure Free Trial  mobikwik@outlook.com
Solution — Subscription ID se switch karo:
bash# Netflix ID
az account show \
  --query "id" \
  --output tsv

# Mobikwik ID
az account show \
  --query "id" \
  --output tsv

Best practice — aliases:
bashecho "alias az-netflix='az account set --subscription \"netflix-sub-id\"'" >> ~/.bashrc
echo "alias az-mobikwik='az account set --subscription \"mobikwik-sub-id\"'" >> ~/.bashrc
source ~/.bashrc

# Ab bas:
az-netflix   # Netflix switch
az-mobikwik  # Mobikwik switch
